Dharvadd kornattok rajeantlea dharvadd jilheachem ani talukeachem mukhel tholl. Hublliche vaivyek sumar 20 kimi. Ontracher ani bellgamvochem agneyek sumar 76 kimi. Ontracher hem xar voslam. Punnem-bengllur hea raxttri-i mohamargauyolem ani relvemargauyolem ek mukhel sthanok. Proxasoki-i, xikxonnik, somskritik ani udeogik kendr mhonnun hea xarachi namna asa. Hangachem somxitoxnn vatauronn, umedichem vatauronn ani bhomvtonnocho pachveochar dongul'leo hankam lagun tachi tulla mohabollexvorakodden korop zata. Adlea kallant hea xarabhomvotonni tottbondi ani panch provexodaram axil'lim. Dekhun kaim togoneanchea motan dharvadd ho xobd dvar ani vatt hea don xobdanchem opbhronxorup asunk zai. Dharravo hea vizoinogorchea eka odhikarean 1403 to hanga kil'lo bandil'lo. Tachea namvauyleanoch hea xarak dharvadd hem namv poddlem oxem kaim togone mantat.

==Xarache char mukhel bhag==

Dharvadd xarache char mukhel bhag poddttat.

    Kil'lo ani tache bhomvtonnocho vatthar,
    mukhel xar
    upnogoram
    novi vosnnuk.

Kil'leache udentek mukhel xar patllil'lem asun dharvadd nogropalika (1856) hi pornni sthanik svorajy somstha. 1961 to dharvadd ani huboilli hea don zumvllea xaranchi mellun ek mohanogoropalika sthapon zali. Dekhun sogllim upnogoram ani noveo vosnnuko dharvadd xarachoch bhag somzotat.

==Itihas==

dharvaddocho purvil'lo itihas choddso mellna. Punn baravea xotmanasaun hea xarache ul'lekh mellttat. Sovo vikromadity hachea1117 chea koril'lea lekhant bhaskorodevo namvachea odhikareachea okhtearint ho vatthar axil'lo oso ul'lekh melltta. Teach kallantlea hombol hangachea korivo lekhant dharvaddoche ul'lekh asat. Oli adiloxahan 1573 to dharvadd xaracher zoit melloilem. Fuddem 1674 to xivaji moharazan tem aplea tabeant ghemeren tacher vizapurocho xek choltalo. 1685t tem morattheankoddlean muojhzhom' hea ourongojhebachea putan ghetlem. Fuddem 1753 meren hem xar muslomananche sot'tekhala axil'lem. Fuddem moratthe, hoidor, ttipu adimni odim'modim fuddem moratthe, hoidor, ttipu adimni odim'modim xotmanant tem brittixamni ghetlem. Bharot svotontr zatkoch hem xar kaim kall mumboi rajeant axil'lem. Fuddem 1960 uprant tacho kornattok rajeant aspavo kelo.

Fornichor, katddecheo vostu, fovo, tandull, nolle, viddeo, hatmagauyolem kapodd hanchea veparakhatir hea xarachim namna asa. Hanga nobhovanni kendr ani zaite loghuudeog asat. Dharvadd hem vidyechem ek mukhel kendr. Hanga zaiteo pornneo toxench noveo xikxonnik somstha asat. Kornattok videapitth (1949) eke dongul'lecher asa. Pornnea somsthamni kornattok mhavidealoi, xetki mhavidealoi, borsttol videaloi, xri zogdoguru xonkrachary somskrit patthxalla, kornattok videavrdhok songh, kornattok histtorika sosaitti, xri murughomotth hea pornnea somsthanchi namna asa. Kornattok histtorika sosaitti purabhilekhovidea hea vixeachem proxikxonn divpi ek videaloi hanga asa. Oxem xikxonn divpi bhartantolim hi eksuri xikxonnosomstha. Kornattok videapitthantoli 'kon'nodd risrch insttittyutt' hi halinchea kallantoli ek somstha asun, he somstheutin prachyovidea vixeantolem zaitea korivo lekhanchem vachon, sonxodhon, sonklon ani sompadon zata. He somsthechem ek purat'ttvi-i songrohaloi asun tatunt korivo lekh, pragoitihasik ovxex ani murti dourleat.

Hea xarant hindu, virxoiv, musloman, parxi, zoin, kristamv adi dhormanche lok rautat. Toxench dor eka dhormachim deullam-i hanga asat. Tatunt durgadevi, dot'tatroi, lokxminarainn, honuman, venkttex hea hindu deullanchi; zum'ma, modni, malapura, barimam' hea moxidinchi ani brittix kallant bandil'li el sextts, dho besel mixon, dho romon kethlik chorch adinchi namna asa.Vixramodhama lagosl'lo xonkustombh (ebelisk) kit'turchea zhuzant moronn ayil'lea odhikareache yadik bandla. Hanga axil'lea pornnea kil'leachi-i borich namna asa. Tebhair brittix kallantleo sorkari imaroti, monoro, sorkari rugnnaloyam ani her karealoyancheo imaroti polloupa sarkeo asat.

